<emphasis id="B970EAFEFFF9F6178C6A3976FA46F210" bold="true" box="[1396,1507,3434,3467]" pageId="61" pageNumber="119">Habitat.</emphasis>
Probably forested habitats. Recorded around sea level.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
